import { useState } from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  MenuItem,
  Select,
  TextField,
  Typography,
  FormControl,
  InputLabel,
  Dialog,
  DialogTitle,
  DialogContent,
  DialogContentText,
  DialogActions
} from "@mui/material";

function App() {
  const [message, setMessage] = useState("");
  const [severity, setSeverity] = useState("");
  const [action, setAction] = useState("");
  const [openDialog, setOpenDialog] = useState(false);

  const handleSubmit = async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    await fetch("http://localhost:5001/send-sms", {
      method: "POST",
      headers: {
        "Content-Type": "application/json"
      },
      body: JSON.stringify({ severity, message, action })
    });
    setMessage("");
    setSeverity("");
    setAction("");
    setOpenDialog(true);
  };

  return (
    <Box sx={{ p: 4, maxWidth: 500, mx: "auto", fontFamily: "sans-serif" }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Send a Complaint ‚ù§Ô∏è
      </Typography>
      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
          <InputLabel id="severity-label">Severity Level</InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="severity-label"
            value={severity}
            label="Severity Level"
            onChange={(e) => setSeverity(e.target.value)}
            required
          >
            <MenuItem value="I'm slight miffed üòû">I'm slight miffed üòû</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="I'm mad üòê">I'm mad üòê</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="I'm MAD . üò°">I'm MAD . üò°</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="I'm shaking in my boots ü§¨">I'm shaking in my boots ü§¨</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="I'm going to implode üî•ü§¨üò°ü§¨üî•">I'm going to implode üî•ü§¨üò°ü§¨üî•</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>

        <TextField
          label="Message"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
          value={message}
          onChange={(e) => setMessage(e.target.value)}
          placeholder="Type your message..."
          required
        />

        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
          <InputLabel id="action-label">
            What can Gyuheon do to make you feel better?
          </InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="action-label"
            value={action}
            label="What can Gyuheon do to make you feel better?"
            onChange={(e) => setAction(e.target.value)}
            required
          >
            <MenuItem value="Call and talk">üìû Call and talk</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Apologize on knees">üôè Apologize on knees</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Send me flowers">üíê Send you flowers</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Give me 10000 kisses">üòòüíã Give you 10000 kisses</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Watch TikToks with me">üì±üòÇ Watch TikToks with you</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Buy me boba">üßã Buy you boba</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>

        <Button
          type="submit"
          variant="contained"
          color="primary"
          fullWidth
          sx={{ mt: 3 }}
        >
          Send üíå
        </Button>
      </form>

      <Dialog open={openDialog} onClose={() => setOpenDialog(false)}>
        <DialogTitle>Message Sent üíñ</DialogTitle>
        <DialogContent>
          <DialogContentText>
            Gyuheon has received your email. He is very sorry for making his
            beautiful, wonderful, kind, sexy girlfriend feel upset. He will read
            your message as soon as he can and get back to you.
          </DialogContentText>
        </DialogContent>
        <DialogActions>
          <Button onClick={() => setOpenDialog(false)} autoFocus>
            Okay üíï
          </Button>
        </DialogActions>
      </Dialog>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default App;
